highlights.text: Chitti (From "Jathi Ratnalu") by Ram Miriyala and Radhan has been on Top Songs Hyderabad the longest, at 66 weeks straight.
Mastaaru Mastaaru by G. V. Prakash and Shweta Mohan is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Hyderabad, up 50 spots at #39.
Sid Sriram has the most spots on Top Songs Hyderabad. Urike Urike is the highest at #6.
Neekemo Andamekkuva by Devi Sri Prasad, Mika Singh, Geetha Madhuri, and Velmurugan is the highest new entry on Top Songs Hyderabad at #15.
